videos.description: Villanova's Eric Paschall leaps up and denies Maliek White on the fast break.
videos.headline: Paschall swats ball away with authority

videos.description: Villanova's Eric Paschall hustles to make a steal and sets up a Phil Booth and-1 layup on the fast break.
videos.headline: Nova turns defense into 3 points

videos.description: Eric Paschall comes up with another steal and takes it all the way himself for a fast-break slam.
videos.headline: Paschall does it all for Nova

videos.description: Villanova's Eric Paschall hits a 3-pointer while being fouled and finishes the 4-point play with a free throw.
videos.headline: Paschall completes the 4-point play
